This paper deals with the automated classification of histopathology images using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of pre-trained models and transfer learning techniques also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also involves image retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) aspects, as it deals with the analysis of digital images.
